text: Abdulxashim Mutalov (born February 14, 1947) is an Uzbekistani politician. He was the 1st Prime Minister of Uzbekistan from January 1992 to December 1995.Vicki L. Hesli. Governments and politics in Russia and the Post-Soviet region. Houghton Mifflin (2006), p. 389. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Prime ministers of Uzbekistan Category:Living people
